@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tmknho(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.08 + tmp + 0.64)))
    v2 = v0
    v1 = (v0 / 0.88)
    tmp = (0.74 - ((tmp + 0.70 * v2 + 0.28) * (v2 + 0.65 + v0 + 0.65)))
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
